amage dealt from a single source to a single permanent or player. For example, if the only damage dealt during the turn was Earthquake, which dealt 5 damage to each of four creatures and two players, then X is 5.£11/7/2014: If Impact Resonance has multiple targets, and some, but not all, of them become illegal before Impact Resonance resolves, Impact Resonance will still deal damage to the remaining legal targets according to the original damage division.','R',NULL,'0.08','0.4','2.38',NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,'R','冲击共振',NULL,'Résonance de l''impact','Verheerender Nachhall','Risonanza dell''Impatto','衝撃の共鳴',NULL,NULL,'Resonancia de impacto',NULL,'瞬间',NULL,'Éphémère','Spontanzauber','Istantaneo','インスタント',NULL,NULL,'Instantáneo',NULL,'冲击共振对任意数量的目标生物造成共X点伤害，你可以任意分配，X为本回合单一来源对单一永久物或牌手造成的伤害中，数量最大者的数值。',NULL,'La Résonance de l''impact inflige X blessures réparties comme vous le désirez entre n''importe quel nombre de créatures ciblées, X étant le nombre le plus élevé de blessures infligées par une source à un permanent ou à un joueur ce tour-ci.','Der Verheerende Nachhall fügt X Schadenspunkte zu, deren Aufteilung auf eine beliebige Anzahl an Kreaturen deiner Wahl du bestimmst, wobei X gleich der größten Menge Schadenspunkte ist, die einer bleibenden Karte oder einem Spieler von einer Quelle in diesem Zug zugefügt wurde.','La Risonanza dell''Impatto infligge X danni divisi a tua scelta tra un qualsiasi numero di creature bersaglio, dove X è l''ammontare di danni maggiore inflitto da una fonte a un permanente o a un giocatore in questo turno.','望む数のクリーチャーを対象とする。衝撃の共鳴はそれらに、Ｘ点のダメージをあなたの望むように分割して与える。Ｘはこのターンに発生源１つがパーマネント１つまたはプレイヤー１人に与えたダメージの最大値に等しい。',NULL,NULL,'La Resonancia de impacto hace X puntos de daño divididos como elijas entre cualquier cantidad de criaturas objetivo, donde X es la mayor cantidad de daño hecho por una única fuente a un permanente o jugador este turno.',NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL),('389554','Imperious Perfect','C14','Creature — Elf Warrior','U','{2}{G}','3','2','2',NULL,'Other Elf creatures you control get +1/+1.£{G}, {T}: Create a 1/1 green Elf Warrior creature token.','#_In a culture of beauty, the most beautiful are worshipped as gods._#',NULL,'Scott M. Fischer','202','5',NULL,'G',NULL,'1','1.72','2.95',NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,'G','骄傲至美',NULL,'Parfaite impérieuse','Gebieterischer Perfekter','Perfetta Autoritaria','傲慢な完全者',NULL,NULL,'Perfecta arrogante',NULL,'生物～妖精／战士',NULL,'Créature : elfe et guerrier','Kreatur — Elf, Krieger','Creatura — Guerriero Elfo','クリーチャー ― エルフ・戦士',NULL,NULL,'Criatura — Guerrero elfo',NULL,'由你操控的其他妖精生物得+1/+1。£{G}，{T}：将一个1/1绿色妖精／战士衍生生物放进战场。',NULL,'Les autres créatures Elfe que vous contrôlez gagnent +1/+1.£{G}, {T} : Mettez sur le champ de bataille un jeton de créature 1/1 verte Elfe et Guerrier.','Andere Elf-Kreaturen, die du kontrollierst, erhalten +1/+1.£{G}, {T}: Bringe einen 1/1 grünen #_(Elf, Krieger)_#-Kreaturenspielstein ins Spiel.','Le altre creature Elfo che controlli prendono +1/+1.£{G}, {T}: Metti sul campo di battaglia una pedina creatura Guerriero Elfo 1/1 verde.','あなたがコントロールする他のエルフ・クリーチャーは＋１/＋１の修整を受ける。£{G}, {T}：緑の１/１のエルフ・戦士・クリーチャー・トークンを１体戦場に出す。',NULL,NULL,'Las otras criaturas Elfo que controlas obtienen +1/+1.£{G}, {T}: Pon en el campo de batalla una ficha de criatura Guerrero Elfo verde 1/1.',NULL,'#_在美感的文化中，会将最美丽者崇敬如神。_#',NULL,'#_Dans une culture basée sur la perfection, les plus beaux sont vénérés comme des dieux._#','#_In einer Kultur der Schönheit werden die Schönsten wie Götter behandelt._#','#_In una cultura che venera la bellezza, i più belli sono adorati come divinità._#','#_美が基準の文明では、最も美しいものは神と崇められる。_#',NULL,NULL,'#_En una cultura basada en la belleza, las más bellas son adoradas como diosas._#',NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL),('389555','Incite Rebellion','C14','Sorcery','R','{4}{R}{R}','6',NULL,NULL,NULL,'For each player, Incite Rebellion deals damage to that player and each creature that player controls equal to the number of creatures they control.','#_Nothing breaks the monotony like a good old-fashioned riot._#',NULL,'Alex Horley-Orlandelli','37','5','£11/7/2014: The damage is dealt simultaneously. If this causes all players to have 0 or less life, the game is a draw.','R',NULL,'0.09','0.33','1.14',NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,'R','煽动叛乱',NULL,'Incitation à la rébellion','Rebellion anzetteln','Incitare alla Ribellione','反乱の扇動',NULL,NULL,'Incitar a la rebelión',NULL,'法术',NULL,'Rituel','Hexerei','Stregoneria','ソーサリー',NULL,NULL,'Conjuro',NULL,'对每位牌手而言，煽动叛乱对该牌手和由该牌手操控的每个生物各造成伤害，其数量等同于由他操控的生物数量。',NULL,'Pour chaque joueur, l''Incitation à la rébellion inflige à ce joueur et à chaque créature que ce joueur contrôle un nombre de blessures égal au nombre de créatures qu''il contrôle.','Für jeden Spieler fügt Rebellion anzetteln diesem Spieler und allen Kreaturen, die dieser Spieler kontrolliert, so viele Schadenspunkte zu, wie er Kreaturen kontrolliert.','Per ogni giocatore, Incitare alla Ribellione infligge a quel giocatore e a ogni creatura controllata da quel giocatore danno pari al numero di creature che controlla.','各プレイヤーにつき、反乱の扇動はそのプレイヤーがコントロールしているクリーチャーの数に等しい点数のダメージをそのプレイヤーとそのプレイヤーがコントロールしている各クリーチャーにそれぞれ与える。',NULL,NULL,'Por cada jugador, Incitar a la rebelión hace a ese jugador y a cada criatura que controla ese jugador una cantidad de daño igual a la cantidad de criaturas que controla.',NULL,'#_想要打破千篇一律的生活，暴乱这个方法虽最为古老，但也最为有效。_#',NULL,'#_Pour rompre la monotonie, rien de tel qu''une bonne vieille émeute._#','#_Nichts vertreibt Langeweile so schnell wie ein guter alter Aufstand._#','#_Niente spezza la monotonia come una buona vecchia sommossa._#','#_退屈を破るのには、昔ながらの騒乱が一番だな。_#',NULL,NULL,'#_Nada rompe la monotonía como un buen disturbio a la antigua usanza._#',NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL),('389556','Infernal Offering','C14','Sorcery','R','{4}{B}','5',NULL,NULL,NULL,'Choose an opponent. You and that player each sacrifice a creature. Each player who sacrificed a creature this way draws two cards.£Choose an opponent. Return a creature card from your graveyard to the battlefield, then that player returns a creature card from their graveyard to the battlefield.',NULL,NULL,'Anthony Palumbo','24','5','£11/7/2014: The sacrifice isn’t optional. If you control at least one creature, you must sacrifice one. If you control no creatures, you won’t sacrifice one and you won’t draw two cards. The same is true for the chosen opponent.£11/7/2014: You choose which creature card you’re returning to the battlefield, then the chosen opponent chooses which creature card they are returning. These choices aren’t made until Infernal Offering resolves. Neither card is a target of Infernal Offering.£11/7/2014: You may choose the same opponent for each of the effects, or you may choose different opponents. None of the affected players are targets of the spell.£11/7/2014: You choose the opponents for each effect as the spell resolves.','B',NULL,'0.14','0.42','1.19',NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,'B','炼狱乐施',NULL,'Offrande infernale','Höllisches Präsent','Offerta Infernale','冥府の捧げ物',NULL,NULL,'Ofrenda infernal',NULL,'法术',NULL,'Rituel','Hexerei','Stregoneria','ソーサリー',NULL,NULL,'Conjuro',NULL,'选择一位对手。你和该牌手各牺牲一个生物。每位以此法牺牲生物的牌手各抓两张牌。£选择一位对手。将一张生物牌从你的坟墓场移回战场，然后该牌手将一张生物牌从他的坟墓场移回战场。',NULL,'Choisissez un adversaire. Ce joueur et vous sacrifiez chacun une créature. Chaque joueur qui a sacrifié une créature de cette manière pioche deux cartes.£Choisissez un adversaire. Renvoyez sur le champ de bataille une carte de créature depuis votre cimetière, puis ce joueur renvoie sur le champ de bataille une carte de créature depuis son cimetière.','Bestimme einen Gegner. Du und dieser Spieler opfert je eine Kreatur. Jeder Spieler, der auf diese Weise eine Kreatur geopfert hat, zieht zwei Karten.£Bestimme einen Gegner. Bringe eine Kreaturenkarte aus deinem Friedhof ins Spiel zurück und dann bringt dieser Spieler eine Kreaturenkarte aus seinem Friedhof ins Spiel zurück.','Scegli un avversario. Tu e quel giocatore sacrificate ognuno una creatura. Ogni giocatore che ha sacrificato una creatura in questo modo pesca due carte.£Scegli un avversario. Rimetti sul campo di battaglia una carta creatura dal tuo cimitero, poi quel giocatore rimette sul campo di battaglia una carta creatura dal suo cimitero.','対戦相手を１人選ぶ。あなたとそのプレイヤーはそれぞれクリーチャーを１体生け贄に捧げる。これによりクリーチャーを生け贄に捧げた各プレイヤーはカードを２枚引く。£対戦相手を１人選ぶ。あなたの墓地にあるクリーチャー・カード１枚を戦場に戻す。その後、そのプレイヤーは自分の墓地にあるクリーチャー・カード１枚を戦場に戻す。',NULL,NULL,'Elige un oponente. Ese jugador y tú sacrifican una criatura cada uno. Cada jugador que sacrificó una criatura de esta manera roba dos cartas.£Elige un oponente. Regresa una carta de criatura de tu cementerio al campo de batalla, luego ese jugador regresa una carta de criatura de su cementerio al campo de batalla.',NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL),('389557','Infinite Reflection','C14','Enchantment — Aura','R','{5}{U}','6',NULL,NULL,NULL,'Enchant creature£When Infinite Reflection enters the battlefield attached to a creature, each other nontoken creature you control becomes a copy of that creature.£Nontoken creatures you control enter the battlefield as a copy of enchanted creature.',NULL,NULL,'Igor Kieryluk','114','5','£5/1/2012: Infinite Reflection can enchant a creature controlled by another player.£5/1/2012: If Infinite Reflection enters the battlefield attached to a creature and then becomes attached to a different creature before its enters-the-battlefield trigger resolves, each other nontoken creature you control will become a copy of the first creature.£5/1/2012: If Infinite Reflection leaves the battlefield or becomes attached to a different creature, none of the copy effects end. Your creatures will still be copies of whatever creature each was a copy of.£5/1/2012: If Infinite Reflection enters the battlefield attached to a token creature, the nontoken creatures that become copies of that creature are not themselves tokens.£5/1/2012: Creatures you control don’t copy whether the enchanted creature is tapped or untapped, whether it has any counters on it, whether it has any Auras and Equipment attached to it, or any noncopy effects that have changed its power, toughness, types, color, or so on.£5/1/2012: Because creatures you control enter the battlefield as a copy of the enchanted creature, any enters-the-battlefield triggered abilities printed on such creatures won’t trigger. However, if the enchanted creature has any enters-the-battlefield triggered abilities, those will trigger.£5/1/2012: Replacement effects that modify how a permanent enters the battlefield are now applied in the following order: control-changing effects (such as Gather Specimens), then copy effects (such as the abilities of Infinite Reflection and Clone), then all other effects.£5/1/2012: If a creature such as Clone is entering the battlefield under your control, there will be two copy effects to apply: the creature’s own and Infinite Reflection’s. No matter what order these effects are applied, the creature will be a copy of the enchanted creature when it enters the battlefield.£5/1/2012: Other enters-the-battlefield replacement abilities printed on the creature entering the battlefield won’t be applied because the creature will already be a copy of the enchanted creature at that point (and therefore it won’t have those abilities). For example, if the enchanted creature is Serra Angel, a creature that normally enters the battlefield tapped will enter the battlefield as an untapped copy of Serra Angel, and a creature that would normally enter the battlefield with counters on it will enter the battlefield as a copy of Serra Angel with no counters.£5/1/2012: External abilities may still affect how a creature enters the battlefield. For example, if your opponent controls Urabrask the Hidden, which reads, in part, “Creatures your opponents control enter the battlefield tapped,” a creature entering the battlefield under your control will be a tapped copy of the enchanted creature.£5/1/2012: If you control more than one Infinite Reflection, you can apply those copy effects in any order. Creatures you control will enter the battlefield as a copy of the one whose copy effect you apply last.','U',NULL,'0.11','0.39','3.18',NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,'U','无限映象',NULL,'Reflets infinis','Unendliche Spiegelung','Riflesso Infinito','無限反射',NULL,NULL,'Reflejo infinito',NULL,'结界～灵气',NULL,'Enchantement : aura','Verzauberung — Aura','Incantesimo — Aura','エンチャント ― オーラ',NULL,NULL,'Encantamiento — Aura',NULL,'结附于生物£当无限映象进战场且结附于生物上时，所有由你操控且非衍生物的其他生物均成为所结附的生物之复制品。£由你操控且非衍生物的生物进战场时是所结附的生物之复制品。',NULL,'Enchanter : créature£Quand les Reflets infinis arrivent sur le champ de bataille attachés à une créature, chaque autre créature non-jeton que vous contrôlez devient une copie de cette créature.£Les créatures non-jeton que vous contrôlez arrivent sur le champ de bataille en tant que copie de la créature enchantée.','Verzaubert eine Kreatur£Wenn Unendliche Spiegelung an eine Kreatur angelegt ins Spiel kommt, werden alle anderen Nichtspielsteinkreaturen, die du kontrollierst, zu einer Kopie dieser Kreatur.£Alle Nichtspielsteinkreaturen, die du kontrollierst, kommen als Kopie der verzauberten Kreatur ins Spiel.','Incanta creatura£Quando il Riflesso Infinito entra nel campo di battaglia assegnato a una creatura, ogni altra creatura non pedina che controlli diventa una copia di quella creatura.£Le creature non pedina che controlli entrano nel campo di battaglia come una copia della creatura incantata.','エンチャント（クリーチャー）£無限反射がクリーチャーにつけられた状態で戦場に出たとき、あなたがコントロールする他のトークンでないクリーチャーは、そのクリーチャーのコピーになる。£あなたがコントロールするトークンでないクリーチャーは、エンチャントされているクリーチャーのコピーとして戦場に出る。',NULL,NULL,'Encantar criatura.£Cuando el Reflejo infinito entre al campo de batalla anexado a una criatura, cada una de las otras criaturas que controlas que no sea fic